snippet.title: Zigglox - Alpha Release trailer - 2022
snippet.description:
Build the tallest tower in Zigglox!
——
Be one of the first to play Zigglox during the Alpha Release for free!
See you on April 7th 2022!
——
Team up with friends or get online and find bricks to build the highest and prettiest tower before the other team ! Beware though, some bricks are ... specials !
——
Want to know more? 
Discord channel: https://discord.gg/dhBgJqHB
Twitter: https://twitter.com/zigglox
Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/zigglox/
Website: https://www.zigglox.com
